Moroccan children find drugs on beach - newspaper . Children playing on a Moroccan beach opened the plastic bag they found and tasted the white powder inside - - 30 kg ( 66 pounds ) of a hard drug believed to be cocaine , the daily l ' Opinion newspaper said on Wednesday . Police , alerted to the find , checked the beach on Tuesday and found two more similar bags , a total of 90 kg ( 198 pounds ) . The newspaper said police were still analysing the haul . 
